Model definition for Books.ReadingPosition. This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Lets you search for books and manage your Google Books library. service. To reduce the data transferred during service requests, you may remove members that contain data elements that your application does not need. action

public String action
Which action caused the reading position to be set. (This is an input-only field.) NEXT_PAGE: Next page event. PREV_PAGE: Previous page event. SCROLL_TO_PAGE: The user dragged the slider to a page. SELECT_CHAPTER: The user selected a chapter from a list and navigated to the chapter's first page. SEARCH_WITHIN_BOOK: The user chose a result from an intra-book search and navigated to that page. CHOSE_BOOKMARK: The user chose a bookmark and navigated to that page.
